metadata.name: Women of Dichotomy
metadata.description: This limited-edition 10,000 PFP Genesis collection, created on the Ethereum (ETH) blockchain, aims to encourage a sense of power and purpose with each avatar. These women symbolize versatility and uniqueness as well as a representation of your inner warrior self. The combination of assets showcase a myriad of regal features, fashion, and attributes that highlight the beautiful, inspiring, and centuries-old story of womanhood in all its layers. PLEASE NOTE: All minted images will reveal at a later date (TBA). Follow our Twitter @WODNFT for live announcements. Don’t forget to tell the world you’ve minted WOD on all your Socials!
